usdSnmpAgent.name: usdSnmpAgent

revisions.description: Added support for proxy enable/disable feature.
Added support for the snmpSetGroup. Added new objects to the Unisphere-Data-SNMP-MIB supporting interface compress, trap severities and trap severity filtering.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdSnmpAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdSnmpAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the SNMP entity component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper Routing Switch family of products.

usdSnmpAgentV1.name: usdSnmpAgentV1
usdSnmpAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 1.x system releases.
usdSnmpAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when SNMPv3 support, View support, and Named Access List support were added.

usdSnmpAgentV2.name: usdSnmpAgentV2
usdSnmpAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.0 thru 2.2 system releases.
usdSnmpAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the usdSnmpInterfaceMode object was added.

usdSnmpAgentV3.name: usdSnmpAgentV3
usdSnmpAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.3 thru 3.1 system releases.
usdSnmpAgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when SNMPv2-MIB.sysORTable support was added.

usdSnmpAgentV4.name: usdSnmpAgentV4
usdSnmpAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.2 system release.
usdSnmpAgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when SNMPv2-MIB.snmpSetGroup support was added and new Unisphere SNMP MIB objects were added supporting interface compress, trap severities and trap severity filtering.

usdSnmpAgentV5.name: usdSnmpAgentV5
usdSnmpAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.3 system releases.
usdSnmpAgentV5.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support for proxy enable/disable was added.

usdSnmpAgentV6.name: usdSnmpAgentV6
usdSnmpAgentV6.productrelease:
Version 6 of the SNMP entity component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SNMP entity component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.4 and subsequent system releases.
usdSnmpAgentV6.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SNMP entity application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
